</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idbdb686ea-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s6671/b/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> $500,000 for the period beginning <date date="1976-07-01">July 1, 1976</date>, and ending <date date="1976-09-30">September 30, 1976</date>;</content>
