<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idbdb686eb-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s6671/b/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> $1,000,000 for the fiscal year ending <date date="1977-09-30">September 30, 1977</date>; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idbdb686ec-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s6671/b/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> such sums as may be necessary for each of the succeeding fiscal years.</content>
